695
00:23:44,523 --> 00:23:48,260
Our aim is to launch
Cool-and-Chic Smart Casual

696
00:23:48,326 --> 00:23:51,229
all office workers can wear,
including those of the Dora-Group.

697
00:23:51,863 --> 00:23:53,265
WOO-JAE'S COOL-AND-CHIC IDEA

698
00:23:53,331 --> 00:23:54,199
What is that?

699
00:23:54,833 --> 00:23:56,468
