-It looks plain.

700
00:23:56,535 --> 00:23:57,736
-…I like…
-It's too plain.

701
00:23:57,803 --> 00:24:00,605
-I really like classic looks.
-Yes.

702
00:24:00,672 --> 00:24:03,275
-The tie makes it look too hot.
-Yeah.

703
00:24:03,341 --> 00:24:04,776
-No, you see…
-It looks too plain.

704
00:24:04,843 --> 00:24:06,178
It's just a dress shirt.

705
00:24:06,745 --> 00:24:07,813
You don't have anything special.

706
00:24:07,879 --> 00:24:09,314
This is a style that I love.

707
00:24:09,381 --> 00:24:11,216
-So that's it.
-What?

708
00:24:11,283 --> 00:24:12,851
Don't you like classic styles?

709
00:24:12,918 --> 00:24:14,519
-I do.
-It looks too hot.

710
00:24:14,586 --> 00:24:16,087
But you need an idea of your own.

711
00:24:16,154 --> 00:24:19,291
-His idea is too plain.
-That is all I prepared.

712
00:24:19,357 --> 00:24:20,725
I have to use the restroom.

713
00:24:20,792 --> 00:24:21,626
Hang on.

714
00:24:23,228 --> 00:24:25,363
-Hang on.
-It's wide open in the back.

715
00:24:25,964 --> 00:24:27,165
There's nothing.

716
00:24:28,600 --> 00:24:30,469
-There's a surprise feature.
-I see.

717
00:24:30,535 --> 00:24:32,704
Let's say you are dating someone

718
00:24:32,771 --> 00:24:35,006
