-Yes.

719
00:24:35,073 --> 00:24:36,842
-Don't you want to leave an impression?
-Yes.

720
00:24:36,908 --> 00:24:40,278
Hey, Jin-kyung. How was work today?

721
00:24:40,345 --> 00:24:41,313
