726
00:24:48,286 --> 00:24:50,288
I like that underwear.

727
00:24:50,355 --> 00:24:51,690
-How charming.
-Yes.

728
00:24:51,756 --> 00:24:53,458
-Can you get on the subway?
-The subway?

729
00:24:53,525 --> 00:24:54,626
-Yes.
-Which line?

730
00:24:55,193 --> 00:24:56,027
Line two.

731
00:24:56,094 --> 00:24:57,429
That would be tricky.

732
00:24:58,029 --> 00:24:59,564
-Is it?
-Line one is okay.

733
00:24:59,631 --> 00:25:01,199
-Line one is okay though?
-Yes.

734
00:25:02,033 --> 00:25:04,536
NEXT UP IS JIN-KYUNG'S PRESENTATION

735
00:25:04,603 --> 00:25:05,437
YOU MUST BE COLD, WOO-YOUNG

736
00:25:05,504 --> 00:25:06,705
-Look at Woo-young.
-Careful.

737
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:10,308
-This looks pretty.
-Yes, it does.

738
00:25:10,375 --> 00:25:13,411
I prepared a black and white look.

739
00:25:13,478 --> 00:25:16,515
First of all, if you wear something
that is too revealing,

740
00:25:16,581 --> 00:25:19,317
